# .env.local
# Local environment variables for Next.js frontend (RAG Q&A Demo)
# Copy or edit as needed for your local development setup.

# === Backend API URL ===
# Used by frontend to proxy API requests (see next.config.ts)
NEXT_PUBLIC_BACKEND_URL=http://localhost:8000

# === Optional: Feature Flags or Frontend-Specific Settings ===
# (Add any frontend-only env vars below as needed)
# Example:
# NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_NAME=RAG Q&A Demo

# === LLM/Embedding API Keys (Frontend should NOT expose secrets) ===
# Do NOT put OpenAI/Anthropic/HF API keys here.
# All secrets must be set in backend/.env and never exposed to the browser.
